## BEM Naming

- Block: `.card`
- Element: `.card__title`, `.card__image`
- Modifier: `.card--featured`, `.button--primary`

---

## Focus & Accessibility

- All interactive elements: visible `:focus-visible` (e.g. 2px outline + 2px offset).
- Skip link: `position: absolute; top: -40px;` then `top: 0` on `:focus`.
- Touch targets: `min-width: 44px; min-height: 44px` for tap areas.

---

## Reduced Motion

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

---

## Performance

- Prefer `transform` and `opacity` for transitions/animations.
- Avoid animating `width`, `height`, `margin` when possible.
- Use `contain: layout style paint` on isolated components where appropriate.
- Use `will-change` sparingly and remove after animation.

All new or edited CSS must use 8px grid values and the project’s design tokens (see `src/styles/global.css`).
